s including orchestration, monitoring, and high availability Beneficial: Experience in blockchain technologies, distributed applications and security protocols Beneficial: Experience with cryptographic systems Scaled the products and technologies of a startup from early on, proven experience of building and shipping security products from prototype to production Track record of leading technical directions, architecture and implementation Skilled communicator both to technologists as well as business stakeholders Outstanding track record of innovation and success Responsibilities Drive Xage\u2019s architectural vision and implementation, decentralized application designs, and security protocols Closely collaborate and partner with the engineering team members Work closely with the product management team, and drive the technology & architectural aspects of the product Align the product with industry security standards, compliance requirements and certifications for the target verticals Evaluate new security protocols & technologies, and understand how to integrate the same into the product "
